@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_bxpwxs(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = v1
    v0 = wp.exp((wp.sin(v1 + 0.19) / v0))
    v0 = 0.63
    v2 = (0.02 - ((tmp + 0.72 / tmp + 0.50) + 0.48))
    v1 = ((wp.sin(v1 + 0.89) * v1) / (0.05 + v2))
    v0 = (tmp / (0.38 * wp.cos(v0 + 0.21)))
    tmp = v2
    tmp = v0
    data[tid] = v0
